            <lg xml:id="TK1090">
<l>uṇṭārka ṇalla taṭunaṟāk kāmampōṟ</l>
<l> kaṇṭār makiḻceyta liṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Unlike boiled honey which yields delight only when it is drunk, love gives pleasure even when looked at.</l>
